                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "POFMA",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Fake-News-and-How-to-Spot-It",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Fake News and How to Spot It",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Fake news is false information that is presented as if it were true.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "How-Fake-News-traditionally-Spreads",
          "level" : 3,
          "text" : "How Fake News (traditionally) Spreads",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Previously, information could only be spread through newspapers, TV, and radio - these limited sources of",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "information restricted the spread of fake news, as the “network” effect was nonexistent.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Back then, fake news usually only spread via circular reporting. Basically:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Source A reports a false story",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Source B reports on Source A’s story, citing it as a source",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Source A then cites Source B as a source",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Or,",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Source A, B, and C all report on a false story",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Source D reports on A, B, and C’s stories, citing them as multiple corroborating sources",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "This is attributed to the rise of vaccine skepticism, due to the spread of a false paper that claimed a link",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "between vaccines and autism.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "There are also times where satire is re-reported as fact.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "How-Fake-News-Spreads-Now",
          "level" : 3,
          "text" : "How Fake News Spreads Now",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The rise of the internet resulted in the rise of user generated content, which has no editorial oversight.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Most people are ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "NOT",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text" : " able to spot fake news, even if they believe they can. This is because most fake",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "news provokes anger, and is also simple to understand. These two turn off the reasoning part of the brain,",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "making it easier to believe.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Mis-vs-Disinformation",
          "level" : 3,
          "text" : "Mis vs Disinformation",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "Misinformation",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " is false information that is spread without the intent to deceive.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "Disinformation",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " is false information that is spread ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "with",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "emphasis"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " the intent to deceive.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "How-to-Spot-Fake-News",
          "level" : 3,
          "text" : "How to Spot Fake News",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Is the source from a well-known outlet?",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Is the source trying to make me angry?",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Where is the information in the source coming from?",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Does the source stand to benefit from me believing the information presented?",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Echo-Chambers-and-Confirmation-Bias",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Echo Chambers and Confirmation Bias",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Echo chambers are is somewhat related to fake news, and is linked to confirmation bias. Basically, it",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "is the idea that you only follow people who share your views, and so you only see content that agrees",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "with you - regardless of it’s factuality.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "People’s brains are wired to ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "not change",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "emphasis"
            },
            {
              "text" : " views once they are formed, and thus information that contradicts",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "them is ignored and information that supports them is amplified.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "We don’t use the part of the brain responsible for reasoning when we’re processing information, rather",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "we use the emotional part. This is because we are social, and it is more “worth it” to be socially accepted",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "than to risk rejection by changing our views.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Steps to avoid echo chambers:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Recognise that you have at least some confirmation bias",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Consider that you may not understand everything (if you can’t explain it, you don’t understand it)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Research and break down the opposing viewpoint",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Digital-Footprint",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Digital Footprint",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Basically you can get in trouble for something you said online, even if you said it a long time ago or",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "said it in a private\/anonymous message.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Everything you post online is permanent because it can be copied by anything with access. As such, every",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "online interaction you have adds to your digital footprint.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Employers or the public (if you’re famous) may look at your digital footprint, and it may affect",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "your employability or public image.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Cleaning-Up-Your-Digital-Footprint",
          "level" : 3,
          "text" : "Cleaning Up Your Digital Footprint",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Be aware of your digital footprint",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "Review old social media accounts and posts to manage your digital footprint.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "Make a list of all past social media accounts and delete those you no longer use, rather than just deactivating them.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Remove potentially embarrassing content that could harm your career or personal life.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "Something being available in an internet archive is better than it being available publicly",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Be discerning about what and where you post online.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "items" : [
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "Regularly evaluate your current social media posts and pictures to ensure they reflect your best self.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "Be mindful of what you share online, as employers may review your social media presence.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "Adjust privacy settings on social media to limit who can see your posts, ideally restricting access to friends only.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "Reassess your friend list to ensure that only trusted individuals have access to your online life.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "content" : [
                        {
                          "inlineContent" : [
                            {
                              "text" : "Consider the potential risks of sharing content, as even private posts can be leaked by friends.",
                              "type" : "text"
                            }
                          ],
                          "type" : "paragraph"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "unorderedList"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "POFMA",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "POFMA",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "POFMA stands for the Protection from Online Falsehoods and Manipulation Act, and it is a law in Singapore that",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "aims to combat the spread of false information online.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "It allows the government to:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Issue corrections to,",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Take down,",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Block accounts which spread false information.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "This generally only applies in two cases:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "The false information has a wide reach (eg. goes viral or is spread by an influencer)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "The false information is likely to cause harm (eg. inciting violence, causing panic, etc.)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "It does NOT apply to:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Opinions, satire, or parody",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Criticism of the government or public officials (NOTE: you can still be sued for defamation, just not under POFMA.)",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "orderedList"
        }
      ],
      "kind" : "content"
    }
